title: Refrigerator Door Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap - Right Side
description: Refrigerator Door Shelf Retainer Bar End Cap - Right Side ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 34 Reviews PartSelect Number PS429668 Manufacturer Part Number 240311502 This replacement bar end cap can be used for a shelf in your freezer. The end cap is 4.25 inches long and 2.4 inches wide. You may need a flat blade screwdriver in order to pop out the existing end cap. Slide the new cap in place, making sure the locking tab is secure, and replace the bar.
